00:36:48.407 --> 00:36:51.532
Aku tidak tahu alamat itu.
Silakan ulangi...


438
00:36:59.241 --> 00:37:01.324
Tolong pakai sabuk pengaman Anda.

439
00:37:34.865 --> 00:37:37.115
